reviews.text: The noodle and congee is in pretty good quality. Also, the chicken ginger stuff is delicious. The steamed fish isn’t that great, don’t know why so many people ordered it.
Food is average. Service is below average. Crowded and uncomfortable.
Food is tasty overall but price pretty expensive

One of the best local bistros which serve good fish congee, glutinous rice dumpling and Cantonese noodles. Price-wise it is more costly than other bistros, but the seats are more comfortable n quality food. That s why it won a Michelin but not the other. Tea time price is good.
Good taste

result.name: Trusty Congee King

reviews.text: 雖然有米推 但服務態度實在不好 對外國人很不友善的一家店 乖乖排隊被插隊 然後不給杯子要了兩次才給 菜單應該有兩份也只給一份 隔壁坐的香港人該有都有 儘管食物還不錯 但服務態度真的不推薦
看起來很像主管的老頭，故意裝作聽不懂普通話，插隊不理，帶位也隨便指，根本不知道坐哪，害我們在裡頭繞，茶杯要了也不給，用碗在喝茶，上了菜看到也不理，魚片粥裡吃到好幾個小魚刺，小孩子吃到怎麼辦！？
👍茶很好喝 食物美味 服務也很好
味道同水準靠得住，份量也足夠。中游價錢，會收茶錢。
招呼一般，坐太窄，但食品質素好，好味！
